---
// 手渡すアトリエ：つくる人 × ビール売り子。作品が手から手へ渡る。
---
<section class="maker section" id="about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="dot"></span>01 — 手渡すアトリエ</p>
    <h2 class="big head reveal d1">つくって、<span class="am">手渡す。
      <svg class="draw-line under" viewBox="0 0 250 18" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true" style="--len:270">
        <path d="M6,12 C55,4 110,15 160,8 C200,3 230,12 244,7" />
      </svg>
    </span></h2>
    <p class="lead reveal d2">作品も、ビールも、自分の手で人に手渡す。<br />それが、稜馬のスタイルです。</p>

    <div class="handoff" data-handoff data-reveal>
      <!-- 小包の軌道（手描きの点線アーチ） -->
      <svg class="arc" viewBox="0 0 320 96" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M12,84 C90,4 230,4 308,84" />
      </svg>

      <!-- 手書き注釈 -->
      <span class="note hand" aria-hidden="true">手から手へ！
        <svg class="n-arrow" viewBox="0 0 44 30" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8,4 C16,14 26,21 38,25 M38,25 l-9,-1 M38,25 l-3,-8" /></svg>
      </span>

      <article class="panel make reveal d1">
        <span class="tape" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="plabel">MAKE</span>
        <span class="ic" aria-hidden="true">🛠️</span>
        <h3>つくる人</h3>
        <p>CG・画像処理・Web・ゲーム。愛知工業大学・水野研究室で、手を動かしてつくっています。</p>
        <ul>
          <li>C++ / OpenGL</li><li>OpenCV</li><li>Astro / TypeScript</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- 手から手へ渡る作品 -->
      <span class="parcel" aria-hidden="true">作品</span>

      <article class="panel sell reveal d3">
        <span class="tape t2" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="plabel">SELL</span>
        <span class="hanko-mini" aria-hidden="true">馬</span>
        <span class="ic" aria-hidden="true">🍺</span>
        <h3>ビール売り子</h3>
        <p>バンテリンドームで、自分をプロデュースして売るビール売り子。届け方まで、ぜんぶ自分ごと。</p>
        <ul>
          <li>自己プロデュース</li><li>現場の熱</li><li>まっすぐ売る</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- 余白の紙吹雪（控えめ） -->
      <span class="cf f1" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="cf f2" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="cf f3" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="cf f4" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </div>

    <p class="more reveal">
      <a class="btn" href="/about">ぼくのことをもっと<span class="ar">→</span></a>
      <span class="more-note hand" aria-hidden="true">現場の話もあるよ！</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <style>
    .maker { position: relative; }
    .head { margin-top: .6rem; }
    .head .am { color: var(--amber-d); position: relative; display: inline-block; }
    .draw-line.under { position: absolute; left: 0; bottom: -.14em; width: 100%; height: .2em; overflow: visible; }
    .draw-line.under path { fill: none; stroke: var(--amber); stroke-width: 7; stroke-linecap: round; opacity: .9; }
    .lead { margin-top: 1rem; }

    .handoff {
      position: relative; margin-top: 3.2rem;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr; align-items: stretch; gap: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    }

    /* 小包が飛ぶ点線アーチ */
    .arc {
      position: absolute; left: 22%; right: 22%; top: -2.4rem; height: 6rem;
      width: 56%; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .arc path {
      fill: none; stroke: var(--amber-d); stroke-width: 3.2; stroke-linecap: round;
      stroke-dasharray: 1 10; opacity: 0; transition: opacity .6s ease .9s;
    }
    .handoff.go .arc path { opacity: .8; }

    .note { position: absolute; left: 50%; top: -4.4rem; transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-3deg); color: var(--scarlet-d); font-size: 1.06rem; z-index: 2; white-space: nowrap; }
    .note .n-arrow { display: block; width: 38px; height: 26px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .note .n-arrow path { fill: none; stroke: var(--scarlet-d); stroke-width: 2.2; stroke-linecap: round; }

    .panel {
      position: relative;
      background: var(--card); border: 2px solid var(--ink); border-radius: var(--r-lg);
      padding: 1.9rem 1.6rem 1.6rem; box-shadow: var(--sh-2);
      transition: transform .2s var(--spring), box-shadow .2s ease;
    }
    .panel.make { transform: rotate(-.8deg); }
    .panel.sell { transform: rotate(.8deg); }
    .panel:hover { transform: translateY(-7px) rotate(0deg); box-shadow: var(--sh-3); }

    .panel .tape { width: 104px; transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-5deg); }
    .panel .tape.t2 { transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(4deg); background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--scarlet) 30%, #fff 36%); }

    .plabel {
      position: absolute; top: .95rem; right: 1.1rem;
      font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: .62rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .18em;
      color: var(--mut); opacity: .75;
    }
    .panel .ic { font-size: 2.2rem; display: block; }
    .panel h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin: .5rem 0 .6rem; }
    .panel h3::after { content: ''; display: block; width: 2.6em; height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; margin-top: .35rem; background: var(--amber); }
    .panel.sell h3::after { background: var(--scarlet); }
    .panel p { color: var(--mut); font-weight: 500; }
    .panel ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .4rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .panel li { font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: .68rem; padding: .25rem .55rem; border-radius: var(--r-sm); background: var(--paper-3); }
    .panel.sell li { background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--scarlet) 14%, var(--paper)); color: var(--scarlet-d); }

    .hanko-mini {
      position: absolute; right: 1rem; bottom: 1rem; width: 32px; height: 32px;
      display: grid; place-items: center; font-family: var(--f-round); font-weight: 700; font-size: .84rem;
      color: #fff; background: var(--scarlet); border-radius: 50%; transform: rotate(-9deg);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px rgba(255,255,255,.4);
    }

    /* 手渡される作品 */
    .parcel {
      align-self: center; z-index: 3;
      display: grid; place-items: center; width: 62px; height: 62px;
      background: var(--amber); color: #3a2606; font-family: var(--f-round); font-weight: 700; font-size: .82rem;
      border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: var(--sh-2); border: 2px solid var(--ink);
      transform: translateX(-140px) rotate(-8deg) scale(.4); opacity: 0;
    }
    /* 小包のミニテープ */
    .parcel::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: -7px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-6deg);
      width: 30px; height: 11px; background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--scarlet) 34%, #fff 34%);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(27,42,74,.16);
    }
    .handoff.go .parcel { animation: pass 1.1s var(--spring) .35s both; }
    @keyframes pass {
      0%   { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-150px) translateY(0) rotate(-30deg) scale(.4); }
      35%  { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-60px) translateY(-46px) rotate(200deg) scale(1.1); }
      70%  { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(40px) translateY(-30px) rotate(340deg) scale(1); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0) translateY(0) rotate(360deg) scale(1); }
    }

    /* 紙吹雪（余白に少しだけ） */
    .cf { position: absolute; width: 11px; height: 11px; border-radius: 2px; z-index: 0; }
    .cf.f1 { top: -1.6rem; left: 6%; background: var(--amber); transform: rotate(22deg); }
    .cf.f2 { top: -2.6rem; right: 9%; background: var(--scarlet); transform: rotate(-16deg); width: 9px; height: 9px; }
    .cf.f3 { bottom: -1.4rem; left: 30%; background: var(--ink); transform: rotate(36deg); width: 8px; height: 8px; opacity: .5; }
    .cf.f4 { bottom: -.6rem; right: 26%; background: var(--amber-l); transform: rotate(-30deg); }

    .more { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.1rem; margin-top: 2.8rem; }
    .more .ar { transition: transform .2s var(--spring); margin-left: .15rem; }
    .btn:hover .ar { transform: translateX(4px); }
    .more-note { position: relative; color: var(--scarlet-d); font-size: 1rem; transform: rotate(-2deg); }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .handoff { grid-template-columns: 1fr; margin-top: 2.4rem; }
      .arc, .note { display: none; }
      .panel.make, .panel.sell { transform: none; }
      .parcel { justify-self: center; margin: -.5rem 0; }
      .handoff.go .parcel { animation: passV 1s var(--spring) .35s both; }
      @keyframes passV { 0% { opacity:0; transform: translateY(-40px) rotate(-30deg) scale(.4);} 60%{opacity:1;transform:translateY(6px) rotate(300deg) scale(1.1);} 100%{opacity:1;transform:none;} }
      .cf.f1 { top: -1.2rem; }
      .cf.f2 { top: -1.8rem; }
      .more { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .8rem; }
    }
  </style>
</section>
